{
  "texts": [
    "This exercise sharpens students' abilities to perform comprehensive literature reviews, synthesize information, and enhance academic writing.",
    "The literature provided is reviewed and critically assessed by the students, ensuring that they engage with the material at a deeper level.Students can also collaborate with ChatGPT in transforming their research findings into engaging infographics and visual presentations.",
    "This process supports the development of skills in visual communication, data synthesis, and presentation.",
    "By inputting their research data into ChatGPT, students receive suggestions for effective visualizations, including charts, tables, and diagrams.",
    "They then use these suggestions to create clear, visually appealing infographics and presentations with the help of design tools.In practicing qualitative data collection, students conduct simulated interviews and focus groups with ChatGPT."
  ]
}